{{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = Segiri |image = Segiri portrait artwork.png |species = [[Keves]]i human |aliases = No. 7 |age = 3rd Term |gender = Female |haircolor = Gray |eyecolor = Red |affiliation = [[Colony 0]] |voiceactorjp = [[Wikipedia:Ai Kayano|Ai Kayano]] |voiceactoreng = [https://www.imdb.com/name/nm8414895/ Brigid Leahy] |appearances = {{XC3}} }} '''Segiri''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|'なぎり}}, ''Nagiri''), also known as '''No. 7''', is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Segiri is the commander of [[Colony 0]], and she can be recruited as a [[Hero]] by completing the [[Hero Quest]] ''[[Inhumanity]]''. She is a [[Keves]]i human with [[Machina]] traits. Her class rank is increased to 20 after completing the Ascension Quest ''[[Invisible Bond]]''.
== Personality == Before meeting the [[Ouroboros]] group, she goes by her given name "No. 7", the incumbent commander of Colony 0. Unlike the other characters in [[Aionios]], her personality is very robotic with an example of her saying "Affirmative" instead of saying "Yes". Initially, she is so dependent on following orders that she can only act independently by envisioning herself as two people, one of which gives orders to the other.
Though projecting herself much like a robot, she is still much human and endearing, especially to her fellow colony members, whom she cares about deeply. She also quickly develops a strong bond with Sena, who helped will her to defy Consul [[F]]'s orders and strike him down.
== Gameplay == Segiri's class is an [[Attacker]] [[Class (XC3)|class]] named [[Machine Assassin]], which focuses on maximizing the effect of debuffs and can spread them to multiple enemies at once.
Segiri's [[Chain Attack (XC3)|Chain Art]] is [[Viscous Venom]], and her Heroic Chain bonus multiplies her TP by 150% when she completes a Chain Order.
