[[File:XC3 Sharpshooter Weapon Icon.png|thumb|The Sharpshooter class icon]] '''Sharpshooter''' is a [[Keves]]i [[Attacker (XC3)|Attacker]] [[class (XC3)|class]] in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Sharpshooter is a simple attacking class that provides the party with additional damage and buffs.
It is only used by [[Mwamba]], and cannot be inherited by [[Ouroboros]] members. It is one of three classes (and the only class apart from DLC) with this distinction. == Class Stats == The Sharpshooter class grants the following multipliers to Mwamba's base stats, and sets his Physical and Ether Defense to the following values.
In practice, these multipliers are always in effect, since Mwamba cannot change classes. Intermediate values are linearly interpolated between the minimum and maximum values, rounding to the nearest percent. Although class multipliers are programmed for every Rank, only the Rank 10 values end up being used. {| class="xc1 centered" width="100%" ! Rank !! HP !! Attack !! Healing Power !! Dexterity !! Agility !! Physical Defense !! Ether Defense |- | 1 || 80% || 95% || 50% || 110% || 90% || 10% || 10% |- | 10 || 82% || 97% || 55% || 115% || 92% || 12% || 12% |- | 20 || 85% || 100% || 60% || 120% || 95% || 15% || 15% |} === Weapon Stats === Mwamba's Attack stat after being modified by the above class stats is further modified by adding the class's weapon stat, which depends on his [[Level (XC3)|Level]], to obtain the final base Attack stat. These weapon stats also determine Mwamba's Critical Rate and Block Rate.<!-- In the exercise of saving space, only every tenth level is displayed --> {| class="xc1 centered" width="60%" ! Level !! Attack !! Critical Rate !! Block Rate |- | 1 || 16 || 5% || 5% |- | 10 || 34 || 5% || 5% |- | 20 || 61 || 6% || 6% |- | 30 || 95 || 6% || 6% |- | 40 || 132 || 7% || 7% |- | 50 || 176 || 8% || 8% |- | 60 || 225 || 8% || 8% |- | 70 || 278 || 9% || 9% |- | 80 || 340 || 9% || 9% |- | 90 || 409 || 10% || 10% |- | 99 || 478 || 10% || 10% |}
